        <mxCell id="2" value="redisocket.v2 引擎內部架構與訊息流（連線層 ＋ Broker／Presence 抽象層）" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
